## Flashcards on your wrist ⌚️

Study any subject in **quick sessions**, right from your Apple Watch.

{#0F766E}Once a deck is on your watch, you don't need your phone to study.{/}

## Spaced repetition 🔁

Cards you **miss** come back **sooner**. Cards you **know** are spaced out further.

{#0F766E}You review what you're about to forget — and skip what you've mastered.{/}

## A set of cards 🃏

A **deck** groups cards around one subject — like *Spanish verbs* or *world capitals*.

{#0F766E}Pick a deck from the list, and you're studying in seconds.{/}

## A minute is plenty ⏱️

Short and **often** beats long and rare.

{#0F766E}A couple of cards while the kettle boils — that's a real session.{/}
